aboutHumangen: Human Gene Co. has started its activities by a group of Bioinformatics, Biochemistry and Genetic experts, since 2016 under the name of Omics Sharif Service Center – located at Sharif University of Technology – in field of big data analysis and Next Generation Sequencing. Nowadays this center is implementing a comprehensive system of analysis and storage of biological data for specialized users including students, research centers, laboratories and geneticists, which its pre-industrial prototype is ready to utilize. The company also has started to work directly with few well-known genetic laboratories providing them with analytical data services since 2016.
